Zhao Peng

00:16:37.960 --> 00:16:41.020
Anda perlu percaya bahwa
mukjizat masih ada di zaman modern.

00:16:41.990 --> 00:16:43.920
Kedokteran modern sangat maju.

00:16:46.610 --> 00:16:48.800
Mungkin Wenxuan akan pulih.

00:16:51.550 --> 00:16:52.480
Minumlah supnya.

